    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The primary validation evidence demonstrates RH < 1 at all five operating points with mean absolute error of 0.038 RH units, well within the 0.10 acceptance threshold. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision that the CFD model reliably identifies worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
